.col-sm-12
    .row
        .col-sm-6
            p Ever left your Garmin running at the end of a ride? All your hard earned averages declined pointelessly? 
            p This simple editor enables you to delete points from the [b end] of a file, and will then recalculate the overall ride data and return a new copy of the file.
            p To start upload a '.tcx' file. You can convert a .fit file to .tcx using <a href="http://connect.garmin.com/"> Garmin Connect's</a> export functionality.
            p <strong>Warning:</strong> This app has only been tested on an Edge 800 (cycle GPS) with firmware 2.6. YMMV, but a Garmin 610 user reported success. 
            | No copy of the data uploaded or processed is kept.

            form
                div(
                    class="btn btn-primary btn-upload" 
                    ngf-select="vm.upload($file)"
                    ng-model="vm.file" 
                    name="file" 
                    ) {{vm.msg}}
                //- button(class="btn btn-success", type="submit", ng-click="vm.submit()") Submit
                
        .col-sm-6
            img(src="upload/edge.jpg" alt="edge 800")

